# ib_bot — EPYC shadow instance

A second copy of the full ib_bot stack runs on the EPYC tower in Portugal, **alongside** the live Finland instance at `213.159.68.39`. This is a **shadow / dev** environment — same code, separate Postgres, **no live trading**, **no IB Gateway connection**. Use it for:

- Testing migrations / new features without touching production.
- Eventual full cut-over once IB Gateway has been moved to EPYC (see "Cutover sequence" below).

Live trading remains on Finland until that ceremony is performed manually.

